    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You attempt to drive a creature you can see within range to distraction, making it less likely to catch pickpockets, discern it is being deceived, or notice your sneaking companions. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or have disadvantage on Wisdom (Insight) and Wisdom (Perception) checks for the duration. The spell ends early if you or your companions do anything harmful to it.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
